title: Decor Avenue Custom Cordless 57 1/2 W x 54 to 60 H Seashell Light Filtering Cellular Shade Inside Mount
features: Decor Avenue Light Filtering shades allow light to pass through the fabric (These are NOT BLACKOUT). These cellular shades offer sound absorption, PROVIDE PRIVACY, energy efficiency during all seasons and give contemporary styling with color coordinated satin smooth headrail and bottom rail. WHITE color on back side of shade fabric to satisfy HOA requirements. PRIVACY FACTOR: 6 out of 10.

THIS IS AN INSIDE MOUNT LISTING. Inside mount means installing inside the window frame. The window frame needs to be at least 1 1/2 inches deep to install as inside mount. Please measure horizontally at the top, middle and bottom, and then order the narrowest measurement and your shade will arrive with a 1/4-inch deduction in the width.

Each 9/16-inch single cell honeycomb cordless cellular shade has a smooth cordless operation. End caps, simple snap-in brackets (that fit for both inside mount and outside mount applications), and mounting hardware is included.
If you are having difficulty ordering, or have any other questions, please feel free to click on our brand name to contact us.
Free color swatches are available upon request.

They have no lift cords and are easy to raise and lower with a light touch. They are designed to offer comfort with privacy, insulation for lower utility bills and sound absorbtion.
